---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 394
  - Title: Quran
    Location: II 216
Tags:
  - Combat-Action=Holy War=Injunction to Holy War
  - 488
---
Warfare is ordained for you. though it is hateful unto you： but it may
be that ye hate a thing which is good for you. and it may be that ye
love a thing which is bad for you. Allâh knoweth. ye know not.
